-- Greenbriar in Venture With Alterra for Puerto Rico Solar
-- B y   J u s t i n   D o o m
-- 2013-04-29T16:10:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-29/greenbriar-in-venture-with-alterra-for-puerto-rico-solar.html
Greenbriar Capital Corp., a
Canadian real-estate and energy developer, formed a joint
venture with  Alterra Power Corp. (AXY)  to develop 100 megawatts of
solar projects in  Puerto Rico .  Greenbriar and Alterra each own 50 percent of AG Solar One,
which will sell electricity to the Puerto Rico Electric Power
Authority, according to a statement today from the Vancouver-
based companies.  AG Solar One may pursue additional renewable-energy
projects in the future.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Justin Doom in New York at 
 jdoom1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reed Landberg at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net  